223
00:11:58,067 --> 00:12:02,067
Just cancel it if it's inviting
unwanted attention.

224
00:12:02,067 --> 00:12:04,233
The aunties are gossiping.

225
00:12:04,233 --> 00:12:05,967
They say it's too much!

226
00:12:05,967 --> 00:12:07,100
Too much?

227
00:12:07,967 --> 00:12:09,800
- Oh, Noa.
- Hi.

228
00:12:10,733 --> 00:12:11,900
Too much?

229
